        <div class="demo-examples">
            <h2 style="color: white; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">üìù Try These Demo Examples</h2>
            
            <div class="demo-card" onclick="loadExample(1)">
                <div class="demo-title">Health Misinformation Example</div>
                <div class="demo-text">"SHOCKING: Scientists ADMIT that drinking lemon water every morning actually CAUSES bone cancer! Share this to save a life!"</div>
            </div>

            <div class="demo-card" onclick="loadExample(2)">
                <div class="demo-title">Political Misinformation Example</div>
                <div class="demo-text">"BREAKING: Government officials SECRETLY meeting to ban all social media by 2025! They don't want you to know this! Share before it's deleted!"</div>
